{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they-- they used to take them out, every day, to work outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a procession of people that were taken out every day, every morning, and came back at night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think I must have stayed with some of the older-- I think they were the younger people that went out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The older people stayed inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But The younger people who could work [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were taken out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was also a sort of a-- like a committee of-- of Jews who actually ran the ghetto on a volu-- obviously on a voluntary basis, who were sort of in charge of things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had some sort of liaison with-- with the authorities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I can't remember what else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But mostly, I remember my parents walking out every day to go to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think my father was on the Jewish council because he seemed to have more information than-- now that I understand what happened-- he seemed to have more information about what was happening than I would imagine anybody else would have.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that may have-- may have made a difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Edward.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
